*Launch.user
*.userosscache
*.rsuser
*.sln.docstates
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 2. Build & Execution Artifacts
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Ignore all bin and obj folders recursively across the solution
**/[Bb]in/
**/[Oo]bj/
**/[Rr]elease*/
**/[Dd]ebug*/
x64/
x86/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]64/
**/publish/
artifacts/
out/
dist/

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. WebView2 Cache & Runtime Environments (CRITICAL)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Blazor Hybrid/MAUI on Windows uses WebView2, which creates a huge, deep cache
# directory under bin/ or build output. Ignoring this prevents deep file indexing
# and long path error exceptions.
**/EBWebView/
**/GabsHybridApp.Maui.exe.WebView2/

